721712f-b.title: Manhattan: Morningside Avenue - 122nd Street (West)
721712f-b.text:
(ie2)
Morningside Avenue, -t, adjoining and south of the S.E.
corner of W. 122nd Street, showing prominently the Morningside
Presbyterian Church. To the left appears an extensive view
eastward on the south side of W. 122nd Street (across Manhattan
and St. Nicholas Avenues, respectively in No. 1).
March 19, 1938.
Views 1 and 2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(3)
No. 3 is a more extensive view southward on the east side
of this thorouchfare.
Auaust 1930.
9eorge L. Palgue
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
